If relevant, please indicate based on your medical judgment if there is a change in treatment intensity of antihypertensive or lipid-lowering medication(s) from randomisation (V2) to week 64 (V19).

The evaluation should be based on whether an overall change has occurred of antihypertensive or lipid-lowering medication(s) (i.e., either increase, decrease or no change) after reviewing all available relevant information e.g., changes in drug dose, drug class, number of drugs or a combination of these.
